{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a306cbb616","title":"视察湖南文化大革命时的一些讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c3bf0daf7a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"a306cbb616","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"华国锋","id":"b42d1ed230","type":"人物"},{"name":"指导理论","id":"c1c0033e04","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"212da9e8f8","type":"title","text":"视察湖南文化大革命时的一些讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3080a8b332","type":"paragraph","text":"视察湖南文化大革命时的一些讲话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a219be0f6f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb5fe3a55f","type":"paragraph","text":"（根据黎源、华国锋、章伯森传达记录整理）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74b0f53256","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.09.00","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73af1f6ece","type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级内部没有根本利害冲突，为什么要分两大派呢？两派要互相少讲别人的缺点，多做自我批评才有利于革命的大联合。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3797fd7574","type":"paragraph","text":"（在谈到群众两派对立时说）两派都是工人，一派造反，一派保守，保守是上头有人蒙蔽了他们，对受蒙蔽的群众不能压。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2524bba3e3","type":"paragraph","text":"（在谈到湘潭情况时说）这样多的产业工人，不会一辈子保皇，要正确对待，至于他们的头头，靠下面自己起来造反。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf10c75b71","type":"paragraph","text":"（在谈到要正确对待干部时说）干部大多数是好的，我们要团结大多数，包括犯过错误向群众做了检讨的，除了极少数坏人，打击面宽了不好，对干部除投敌、叛变、自首者外，过去十几年，几十年总做过一些好事嘛！要扩大教育面，缩小打击面，进行批判斗争时，要用文斗，不要武斗，不要侮辱。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4efd328b00","type":"paragraph","text":"（在谈到造反派要加强学习时说）对造反派也要进行教育，现在正是犯错误的时候。青年人不要性急，现在紧张、严肃有余，团结、活泼不足，缺乏民主作风，不平等待人，打人骂人拍桌子，把我们的情况搞乱了，把我们坚持团结──批评──团结的公式搞乱了。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a306cbb616","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}